trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey.Dispose%2A> when you are finished using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey.Dispose%2A> 使用完畢時，請呼叫 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey.Dispose%2A> method leaves the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey.Dispose%2A> 方法會將 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman> 保留在無法使用的狀態。

trans-unit.source: After calling <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey.Dispose%2A>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: 在呼叫<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey.Dispose%2A>，您必須釋放所有參考<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman>讓記憶體回收行程可以回收記憶體的<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman>所佔用。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[清除 Unmanaged 資源上](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md)和[實作 Dispose 方法](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md)。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman" /> class and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: 釋放 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman" /> 類別所使用的 Unmanaged 資源，並選擇性地釋放 Managed 資源。

trans-unit.source: This method executes in two distinct scenarios:
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行兩個不同的案例中：

trans-unit.source: If `disposing` equals `true`, the method has been called directly or indirectly by a user's code.
trans-unit.target: 如果`disposing`等於`true`，已經呼叫方法直接或間接透過使用者程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Managed and unmanaged resources can be disposed.
trans-unit.target: 管理，而且可以處置 unmanaged 的資源。

trans-unit.source: If `disposing` equals `false`, the method has been called by the runtime from inside the finalizer, and you should not reference managed resources.
trans-unit.target: 如果`disposing`等於`false`、 完成項，在執行階段呼叫的方法，而且您不應該參考 managed 的資源。

trans-unit.source: Only unmanaged resources can be disposed.
trans-unit.target: 可以處置 unmanaged 的資源。

trans-unit.source: If you need to provide cleanup code for managed and unmanaged resources that an object created, you should override this method.
trans-unit.target: 如果您需要提供建立物件的 managed 和 unmanaged 資源的清除程式碼，您應該覆寫這個方法。

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會呼叫公用`Dispose()`方法和<xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()` 叫用受保護`Dispose(Boolean)`方法`disposing`參數設定為`true`。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> 叫用`Dispose`與`disposing`設`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey> references.
trans-unit.target: 當`disposing`參數為 true，這個方法的任何 managed 物件所持有的資源全部釋出這個<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey>參考。

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會叫用每個參考物件的 `Dispose()` 方法。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Dispose" /> can be called multiple times by other objects.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Dispose" /> 可以被其他物件呼叫多次。

trans-unit.source: When overriding <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" /> be careful not to reference objects that have been previously disposed of in an earlier call to <see langword="Dispose" />.
trans-unit.target: 在覆寫<see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />小心不要參考物件已處置過的早期呼叫中<see langword="Dispose" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關如何實作<see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />，請參閱[實作 Dispose 方法](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about <see langword="Dispose" /> and <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關<see langword="Dispose" />和<see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />，請參閱[清除 Unmanaged 資源上](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md)。
